                    <li class="mb-2 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-300">Programming Insights: Deep dives into
                        .Net, Typescript, Python, and frameworks like React, Anglular, and Vue.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-300">Data Science Adventures: Exploring
                        machine learning, statistics, and data visualization.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-300">With the help of R and Python, we can
                        perform data analysis and visualization using tools like ggplot2, D3js and Shiny as well as
                        other research-focused tools.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-300">Tech Innovations: The latest trends,
                        tools, and technologies shaping development.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-300">Explore the fascinating world of web
                        development and framework tools like Typescript based frameworks like Angular, React, and Vue as
                        well as their tools and libraries.</li>
                    <li class="mb-2 hover:text-indigo-700 transition duration-300">Getting to know PHP and how it can be
